{"tid":839521,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】《無法無天飛車黨》","createTime":"2018-09-28T04:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T22:48:48.000Z","uid":212112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04952a9abe389ab1130467845d16634f412d3736","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120544_273326dd24754584a7a286151b061c9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120544_273326dd24754584a7a286151b061c9d.png&h=246b5b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情講述主角是一名高級文員，他偕妻子和妹妹乘坐渡輪往離島渡假。同船而往者，有三十多個流氓男女。彼等喜歡以飛車尋求刺激，無法無天，因而被人們稱為「飛車黨」；他們首領是個冷酷青年，其弟有自大狂及虐待狂，且最愛闖禍搗亂。他們在船上見到主角妹妹竟出言調戲。既抵離島，主角三人便赴一間獨處別墅。該別墅是妹妹男友獨自居住。主角遂駕著妹妹男友的汽車，載著妻子和妹妹到野外兜風，但屢遭飛車黨的整蠱，使兩女飽受虛驚。<br />\n當時的離島未設置警署，水警輪每早九時始來巡邏一次，星期天休息。周末，主角無從報警。當夜，主角四人聚在屋裏吃海鮮，飛車黨在郊外紮營。因飛車黨徒有二十二男，九女，首領便叫男黨員們，以比賽飛車技術來決定誰能佔有黨女。結果其弟等十三人遭淘汰，其他男女則在蓬帳裏胡天胡地大被同眠。首領弟他們玩得無聊，便走到主角們的別墅來搗亂。主角等人好不容易才將他們驅走。妻子不勝其擾，翌晨便要回去。妹妹男友不敢強留，準備送他們搭早船，卻發現車胎拆掉。無可奈何中，他們決定動用快艇，但發覺快艇亦已被飛仔們駛往海中。妹妹男友與主角立即駕著一艘小木船出海，準備將快艇弄回來，在海面上跟飛車黨發生沖突。此際，首領弟乘機率領數黨徒衝進別墅。結果，主角妻遭姦污，妹妹也在與黨徒糾纏中喪命.....<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120547_99276be9eb5180b7ffaae3c11ef08dc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120547_99276be9eb5180b7ffaae3c11ef08dc1.png&h=73ebf17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用現今的視野來看這76年的飛車黨仇殺港片很明顯是改編經典復仇電影《殺人不分左右》和《straw dog》，但是這並不影響觀影看本片的爽快感。桂治洪固有的邪異氛圍依舊出色，難得桂導連拍古惑仔都可以拍出詭異cult味之餘亦能像《成記茶樓》一樣探討當時社會問題，法律總是不夠力，以暴制暴，無疑是最公正的解決方式。香港cult王之王桂治洪當之無愧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120549_dffed0fea3bf7970f39a3852620de9ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120549_dffed0fea3bf7970f39a3852620de9ab.png&h=5354aac2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120550_4a1889ef5c0abf637da265f2c44a010b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120550_4a1889ef5c0abf637da265f2c44a010b.png&h=d43a2363&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120552_a092e4c5a819504de91823c55e13f7ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120552_a092e4c5a819504de91823c55e13f7ae.png&h=2d0e56f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120556_9ff7dba74b8e1e621b628e26d906471a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120556_9ff7dba74b8e1e621b628e26d906471a.png&h=488854c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120558_029c7ae562e1f3e5ce8c524e5901612a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120558_029c7ae562e1f3e5ce8c524e5901612a.png&h=d454893b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120559_7c1497b1a44f4557bed9d38ed4f2aade.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120559_7c1497b1a44f4557bed9d38ed4f2aade.png&h=94634127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/Bm74W5ZFtOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm74W5ZFtOI%2F&d=35VR44aBLSg6O01mXEyuI8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3bf1dac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBm74W5ZFtOI%2F&h=1a069c6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/Bm74W5ZFtOI/</a>"},{"pid":"c02462e41b93330beedc4f86d2cc044f3e10f2d4","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/120932_99276be9eb5180b7ffaae3c11ef08dc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F120932_99276be9eb5180b7ffaae3c11ef08dc1.png&h=ce3cdd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我第一次睇見哩張劇照果陣即刻諗起昭和時期幪面超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26108dc7cfd93d254e5826ca9a7ce218bd8a83c","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34afaa5a36eb71b7dfab2cd44fb8acfdcfe849ef","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693a3ef783225f498bf963b843c43f5c5a945584","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f644dc83443ee622c04c8a2047763960880e2dfc","tid":839521,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"七十年代好多呢啲戲，好正"},{"pid":"b3a3f37de33ef32d3446897488fdfbaf9d4292b5","tid":839521,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"咁結局係點架?<br />\n主角有冇殺晒班飛車黨報仇?"},{"pid":"5ced93fa8c4ec407832ecba2cce8f899dcb75aff","tid":839521,"uid":2379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"有無link 好似好正"},{"pid":"3c78887b94a18b297a3145cb9e67afcfccec6502","tid":839521,"uid":212112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3a3f37de33ef32d3446897488fdfbaf9d4292b5","tid":839521,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"咁結局係點架?<br />\n主角有冇殺晒班飛車黨報仇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"我記得結尾大約係飛車黨首領失手撞死了自己弟弟。 <br />\n男女主角殺晒所有飛車黨<br />\n片尾字幕交待男女